ding and for answering such a diverse range of questions. As usual, you will be sent a transcript to check for accuracy following the meeting, but thank you very much to the three of you for your time this morning.&#10;Speaker: Julie Morgan AM&#10;Content: Thank you very much, and thank you for all">
